939'''\n|align=\"center\"|'''1 618 551'''\n|align=\"center\"|'''1 592 795'''\n|align=\"center\"|'''1 407 015'''\n|align=\"center\"|\n|}\n\n==References==\n<references/>\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.twojatwarzbrzmiznajomo.polsat.pl/ Official website]\n\n[[Category:2014 Polish television series debuts]]\n[[Category:Polish television series]]\n[[Category:Your Face Sounds Familiar]]\n[[Category:2010s Polish television series]]\n[[Category:Polsat shows]]\n", "text_old": "{{About||other versions of this series|Your Face Sounds Familiar|the current season|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 13)}}\n\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name          = Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo\n| image              = \n| genre              = [[Reality Television|Reality]]\n| picture_format     = [[16:9]] ([[High-definition television|HDTV]])\n| audio_format       = [[Stereo]]\n| runtime            = \n| presenter          = [[Piotr G\u0105sowski]] <br> Maciej Dowbor \n| judges             = [[Ma\u0142gorzata Walewska]] <small>(''1\u2013'')</small><br/>[[Katarzyna Skrzynecka]] <small>(''2\u2013'')</small><br/>Kacper Kuszewski <small>(''9\u2013'')</small><br>Adam Strycharczuk <small>(''13\u2013'')</small><br/>Pawe\u0142 Kr\u00f3likowski <small>(''1\u201312'')</small><br/></small>[[Bart\u0142omiej Kasprzykowski]] <small>(''5\u20138'')</small><br>DJ Adamus <small>(''1\u20134'')</small><br/>Katarzyna Kwiatkowska <small>(''1'')</small>\n| country            = Poland\n| language           = Polish\n| network            = [[Polsat]]\n| num_seasons        = 13\n| num_episodes       = 131\n| location           = \n| executive_producer = \n| first_aired        = 8 March 2014\n| last_aired         = present\n| producer           = \n| related            = \n| website            = \n| website_title      = \n}}\n\n'''''Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo''''' is a Polish [[talent show]] developed by [[Polsat]] and based on the [[Your Face Sounds Familiar|Spanish]] series. The show is presented by [[Piotr G\u0105sowski]] and Maciej Dowbor, whilst the judging panel consists of Kacper Kuszewski, [[Ma\u0142gorzata Walewska]], Adam Strycharczuk and [[Katarzyna Skrzynecka]].\n\nThe show involves eight celebrities (singers, actors and television personalities) portraying various iconic singers each week to win 10,000 PLN for their chosen charity.\n\n==Format==\nThe show challenges celebrities (singers and actors) to impersonate different music artists every week, which are chosen by the show's \"Randomiser\". Afterwards they are judged by the panel of celebrity judges. The 'randomiser' can choose any older or younger artist available in the machine, or even a singer of the opposite sex, or a deceased singer. The winner of each episode wins 10,000 PLN, and the winner of the whole show wins 100,000 PLN. All money goes for a charity of their choice.\n\n===Voting===\nThe contestants are awarded points from the judges (and each other) based on their singing and dance routines. The points go from 1 to 7 and 10, with 10 being the judge's favorite of the night. After that, each contestant gives 5 points to a fellow contestant of their choice (known as \"Bonus\" points). The judges' score is combined with the \"Bonus\" points.\n\n==Cast==\n\n===Hosts===\n;Key\n:{{Color box|orange|border=darkgray}} Main host\n:{{Color box|lightblue|border=darkgray}} Contestant\n:{{Color box|#ffc6c6|border=darkgray}} Back-up host\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! width=\"180\" rowspan=\"2\"| Host !! colspan=13 text-align:center;| Season\n|-\n! width=\"70\" |1 !! width=\"70\" |2 !! width=\"70\" |3 !! width=\"70\" |4 !! width=\"70\" |5 !! width=\"70\" |6 !! width=\"70\" |7 !! width=\"70\" |8 !! width=\"70\" |9 !! width=\"70\" |10 !! width=\"70\" |11 !! width=\"70\" |12 !! width=\"70\" |13\n|-\n| [[Piotr G\u0105sowski]]|| colspan=13 style=\"text-align:center; background:orange;\"| \n|-\n| Maciej Dowbor|| colspan=13 style=\"text-align:center; background:orange;\"| \n|-\n| Zofia Zborowska||  colspan=3 style=\"text-alig