mber 2015\n| 8\n| 10\n| [[Bart\u0142omiej Kasprzykowski]]\n| Zofia Zborowska\n| Monika Dryl\n| [[Michal (singer)|Micha\u0142 Kwiatkowski]]\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 5)|5) Spring 2016]]\n| 12 March 2016 \u2013 14 May 2016\n| 8\n| 10\n| [[Aleksandra Szwed]]\n| Dariusz Kordek\n| Jerzy Grzechnik\n| [[Katarzyna Pakosi\u0144ska]]\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 6)|6) Fall 2016]]\n| 3 September 2016 \u2013 19 November 2016\n| 8\n| 10\n| Maria Tyszkiewicz\n| Olga Szoma\u0144ska\n| Kamil Bijo\u015b\n| Micha\u0142 Ruda\u015b\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 7)|7) Spring 2017]]\n| 4 March 2017 \u2013 6 May 2017\n| 8\n| 10\n| [[Kasia Popowska|Katarzyna Popowska]]\n| [[Joanna Jab\u0142czy\u0144ska]]\n| S\u0142awomir Zapa\u0142a\n| [[Zofia Nowakowska]]\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 8)|8) Fall 2017]]\n| 9 September 2017 \u2013 11 November 2017\n| 8\n| 10\n| Kacper Kuszewski\n| Krzysztof Antkowiak\n| [[Anna Dereszowska]]\n| Beata Olga Kowalska\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 9)|9) Spring 2018]]\n| 3 March 2018 \u2013 19 May 2018\n| 8\n| 10\n| Filip Lato\n| Jan Traczyk\n| [[Anna Guzik]]\n| Krzysztof Szczepaniak\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 10)|10) Fall 2018]]\n| 8 September 2018 \u2013 17 November 2018\n| 8\n| 10\n| Mateusz Zi\u00f3\u0142ko\n| Rafa\u0142 Szatan\n| Marek Molak\n| Adriana Kalska\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 11)|11) Spring 2019]]\n| 23 February 2019 \u2013 18 May 2019\n| 8\n| 12\n| Kazimierz Mazur\n| [[Katarzyna D\u0105browska]]\n| [[El\u017cbieta Romanowska]]\n| Antoni Smykiewicz\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 12)|12) Fall 2019]]\n| 7 September 2019 \u2013 23 November 2019\n| 8\n| 12\n| Adam Strycharczuk\n| Emilia Komarnicka-Klynstra\n| [[Ewelina Lisowska]]\n| \u0141ukasz Zagrobelny\n|-\n| [[Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 13)|13) Spring-Fall 2020]]\n| 7 March 2020 - 14 March 2020<br>5 September 2020 - 24 October 2020\n| 8\n| 10\n| \n| \n| \n| \n|}\n\n===Season 1 (2014)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 1)}}\nThe first season premiered on March 8, 2014. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Paulina Ignasiak, Julia Pietrucha, Katarzyna Skrzynecka, Agnieszka W\u0142odarczyk\n* Bilguun Ariunbaatar, Artur Chamski, Mariusz Totoszko, Pawe\u0142 Tucholski\n\n===Season 2 (2014)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 2)}}\nThe second season premiered on September 6, 2014. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Maja Bohosiewicz, Joanna Liszowska, Barbara Melzer, Magda Steczkowska\n* Marek Kaliszuk, Jacek Kawalec, Jakub Mol\u0119da, Marcin Przybylski\n\n===Season 3 (2015)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 3)}}\nThe third season premiered on March 7, 2015. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Katarzyna Ankudowicz, Katarzyna Cerekwicka, Anna Czartoryska-Niemczycka, Kaja Paschalska\n* Mateusz Jakubiec, Robert Rozmus, Stefano Terrazzino, Grzegorz Wilk\n\n===Season 4 (2015)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 4)}}\nThe fourth season premiered on September 5, 2015. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Monika Dryl, Katarzyna Glinka, Natalia Szroeder, Zofia Zborowska\n* Micha\u0142 Grobelny, Bart\u0142omiej Kasprzykowski, Micha\u0142 Kwiatkowski, Krzysztof Respondek\n\n===Season 5 (2016)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 5)}}\nThe fifth season premiered on March 12, 2016. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Katarzyna Pakosi\u0144ska, Aleksandra Szwed, Agnieszka Twardowska, Katarzyna Zieli\u0144ska\n* Adam Fidusiewicz, Jerzy Grzechnik, Dariusz Kordek, Marcin Rogacewicz\n\n===Season 6 (2016)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 6)}}\nThe sixth season premiered on September 3, 2016. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Olga Borys, Joanna Moro, Olga Szoma\u0144ska, Maria Tyszkiewicz\n* Mateusz Banasiuk, Kamil Bijo\u015b, Rados\u0142aw Pazura, Micha\u0142 Ruda\u015b\n\n===Season 7 (2017)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 7)}}\nThe seventh season premiered on March 4, 2017. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Monika Borzym, Joanna Jab\u0142czy\u0144ska, Zofia Nowakowska, Katarzyna Popowska\n* Pawe\u0142 Jasionowski, Krzysztof Kwiatkowski, Jakub \u015awiderski, S\u0142awomir Zapa\u0142a\n\n===Season 8 (2017)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 8)}}\nThe eighth season premiered on September 9, 2017. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Anna Dereszowska, Aleksandra Gintrowska, Beata Olga Kowalska, Katarzyna Mo\u015b\n* Krzysztof Antkowiak, Kacper Kuszewski, Mariusz Ostrowski, Marcel Sabat\n\n===Season 9 (2018)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 9)}}\nThe ninth season premiered on March 3, 2018. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Anna Guzik, Natalia Krakowiak, Joanna Lazer, Izabella Miko\n* Filip Lato, Andrzej M\u0142ynarczyk, Krzysztof Szczepaniak, Jan Traczyk\n\n===Season 10 (2018)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 10)}}\nThe tenth season premiered on September 8, 2018. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Adriana Kalska, Katarzyna Maci\u0105g, Honorata Skarbek, Michalina Sosna\n* Marek Molak, Bogumi\u0142 Romanowski, Rafa\u0142 Szatan, Mateusz Zi\u00f3\u0142ko\n\n===Season 11 (2019)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 11)}}\nThe eleventh season premiered on February 23, 2019. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Katarzyna D\u0105browska, Iga Krefft, El\u017cbieta Romanowska, Marta Wiejak\n* Stanis\u0142aw Karpiel-Bu\u0142ecka, Kazimierz Mazur, Kamil Pawelski, Antoni Smykiewicz\n\n===Season 12 (2019)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 12)}}\nThe twelfth season premiered on September 7, 2019. The contestants were four women and four men:\n\n* Emilia Komarnicka-Klynstra, Ewelina Lisowska, Katarzyna Ptasi\u0144ska, Ewelina Ruckgaber\n* Robert Koszucki, Jeremi Sikorski, Adam Strycharczuk, \u0141ukasz Zagrobelny\n\n===Season 13 (2020)===\n{{Main|Twoja twarz brzmi znajomo (season 13)}}\nThe thirteenth season will premiere on March 7, 2020. The contestants are four women and four men:\n\n* Ma\u0142gorzata Andrzejewicz, Natalia Avelon, Kamila Boruta, Marta Ga\u0142uszewska\n* Pawe\u0142 Dudek, Karol Dziuba, Filip Gur\u0142acz, Maurycy Popiel\n\n==Viewing figures==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Episode\n!Season 1\n!Season 2\n!Season 3\n!Season 4\n!Season 5\n!Season 6\n!Season 7\n!Season 8\n!Season 9\n!Season 10\n!Season 11\n!Season 12\n!Season 13\n|---\n|align=\"center\"|'''1'''\n|align=\"center\"|2 804 932 <br> <small>(March 8, 2014)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 350 645 <br> <small>(September 6, 2014)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 898 003 <br> <small>(March 7, 2015)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 160 415 <br> <small>(September 5, 2015)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 370 186 <br> <small>(March 12, 2016)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 012 816 <br> <small>(September 3, 2016)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 945 902 <br> <small>(March 4, 2017)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 423 830 <br> <small>(September 9, 2017)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 846 549<br> <small>(March 3, 2018)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 288 626<br> <small>(September 8, 2018)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 501 097<br> <small>(February 23, 2019)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 264 579<br> <small>(September 7, 2019)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 449 657<br> <small>(March 7, 2020)</small>\n|---\n|align=\"center\"|'''2'''\n|align=\"center\"|2 728 234 <br> <small>(March 15, 2014)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 214 927 <br> <small>(September 13, 2014)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 742 968 <br> <small>(March 14, 2015)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 060 038 <br> <small>(September 12, 2015)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 284 325 <br> <small>(March 19, 2016)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 883 449 <br> <small>(September 10, 2016)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|2 013 568 <br> <small>(March 11, 2017)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 532 485<br> <small>(September 16, 2017)</small>\n|align=\"center\"|1 483 2